{\b \pard\qj\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 Simple Structure} The topology structure of neural oscillator is simple, it includes one attractive limit circle and one fix repellor.\par
{\b \pard\qj\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 Large Basin of Attraction} All the simulations we carried out converged to the same limited circle.\par
{\b \pard\qj\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 Fast Converging Speed} In most of the case, the flow will converge to the limit circle within one period time.\par
